Hello @Abhishek Choudary sir i have made a palindrome word checker we have to right a word in the
text box below and submit it then it will show that the text is Palindrome or not 
you can also run the below code in your device you can check it if it wrong or not.And i have uploaded a video in JavaScript Essntials Program JUL 2021 a video you can check it
 
 <!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Fionation</title>
</head>
<body>
    Enter any word i can check it if it is Palindrome or not.<br><br>
    Enter Any String :<input type="text" id="a"><br><br>
    Result String :<input type="text" id="b"><br><br>
    <input type="Submit" onclick="pal()"><br><br>
    <script type="text/javascript">
    function pal()
       {
    
        var x=document.getElementById("a").value;
            var y="";
            for(i=x.length-1;i>=0;i--)
                {
                     y=y+x[i];
                }
            if(x==y)
               document.getElementById("b").value=y+" is a Palindrome ";
            else
                document.getElementById("b").value=y+" is not a Palindrome ";
       }
       </script>
</body>
</html>
 
